<Content>The fact this device will only work with XP/MediaPlayer 10 makes this player a major pain. Go over to a buddy's and think you will drag and drop his mp3's to your player, they better have the newest setup! Ditto at your work ect.. It has really been a pain. Sound quality is great, battery life is ok(AAA)and I really like the size/shape. I really wish i had read the fine print, but i thought it's iriver they will have all kinds of firmware upgrades, Nope not anymore they have sold out to Microsoft.   
