<Review ID>8009900
<Product Name>iRiver T30 1 GB MP3 Player
<Title>The key that opens the door to YOUR Music!
<Date>Fri Jan 20 00:00:00 CST 2006
<Content>The iRiver T30 1GB MP3 Player is a blessing in disguise!  Small and compact, it's durability and feature's are something that shine in a market full of options...  With 1GB you can get a slew of song's downloaded into it.  USB cable included, so within 10 minutes I had variety of favorite song's downloaded and was ready to hit the gym!  I use my iRiver when biking, running, and working out at the gym, as well as sitting on a long plane or car ride.  The headphone's are nice and have thicker than normal insulation around the wire's providing more wear and tear protection over time (headphone wires, as you know, can short out with a mere twist).  The buttons are easy to navigate and the but the instruction manual will come in handy when you first get it.  I also got a belt clip as well as the lanyard for wearing it around my neck like if you're on an airplane.  The armband carriage is great for working out at the gym.  For just a few dollars more I decided to go with this one instead of a 512.  You won't be disappointed as a gig holds twice the number of songs.  I also enjoy audiobook's on it as well.    The only thing I didn't like was that you couldn't pick from a variety of colors, but all thing's considered, you're not buying it because of it's looks in that regard; you're buying it so you can have hassle-free enjoyment of you're favorite music anywhere you go!  
<Overall>5

